@@TJvLocalFileUrlGrabber
Summary
  This a grabber for Local File URLs
Description
  This grabber handles Local File URLs, that is URLs that start with 'file://', '?:\' or '\\'
  Local is in opposition to Internet and refers to files on a computer as well as to files on
  the local network.


----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvLocalFileUrlGrabber.PreserveAttributes
Summary
  If True, the attributes of the source file will be copied to the destination file. Attributes are
  the date, the read-only and hidden properties.


----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvLocalFileUrlGrabber.CanGrab
Summary
  Return true if the URL is a Local File URL
Parameters
